Dialogs.Dialog: Somehow, I feel like you're distracted...
Are you thinking about something else？
Could it be that... you're mad at me？
Don't you want to go home？
Hehe. Got something to think about？
Hehe, you know what to do now, right？
I don't mind us holding hands. What do you say？
Hehe, you don't have to be that nervous.
Yeah, it's like I can feel the warmth of your body...
No. It's just... Your hand is unexpectedly warm... Hehe.
So this is what it feels like to hold a guy's hand. My heart is throbbing. Hehe.
No, that's not the case. I was thinking that you are a man, and...
Can you hold my hand tightly？
...Hehe, I thought you would squeeze my hand until it hurts. Too bad. Hehe.
Right, right. Like that. I'm happy.
Why am I feeling so happy like this...？
We're just holding hands... This is weird... but it feels good.
...Hehe, my heart is throbbing. Look... Isn't my face all red？
When you hold my hand, I can feel the warmth going through my heart.
You holding my hand. I can feel the touch from your palm and your fingers. This is such a success.
Hehe. Something a little cheesy like this is okay, right？
That we're holding hands like this. We're really like lovers, right？
We're just holding hands. I wonder if it can be even more exciting if we get closer.
My heart... It won't listen to my orders anymore...
Do we... Never mind, it's nothing.
Of course. However I look at it, we are lovers.
We're lovers, so this is natural, right？ ...Come on.
When we hold hands, no matter how people look at us, we look like lovers, right？
I feel like it's a bit unfortunate that we've arrived this soon...
What a great time, it went by so quickly...
Someone here just doesn't want to hold my hand. Isn't that regrettable？
I kind of wanted to hold hands with you.
Ah, look there. Doesn't that house have a very nice garden？
Hehe. Although I want you to always keep your eyes on me, it's such a waste if you don't look at your surroundings at all.
Ah, that house's reconstruction has finished.
Look at the nameplate. It's made of wood and has a heart mark on it... Is it handmade？
You're right. Could it be that they're newlyweds？
Hehe. It would be nice to have something like that when we build our home.
Hey, look at that apartment. It looks like the ones you see in old movies, huh？
It looks like it was built in the Showa era, right？
I wonder if there's a public bath nearby.
Eh？ I think people who lived in apartments in the Showa era relied on public baths, right？
Ah... That mansion... I think I've seen it in a movie.
Look, right there. I know I've seen that balcony from somewhere before.
That one？ It looks like a nice mansion... Do you remember which movie you saw it from？
I think it was a horror movie where the whole family became ghosts... Hmm, which one was that？
Ah... Hey, hey. Do you think that old house feels nice？
Eh？ Don't you think it somehow belongs in a horror movie？
Well... I was thinking it was like a witch's hut.
But it's too bad that it doesn't have a chimney. That's disappointing.
Ah... Look, there's a pair of little birds on the power cable.
Hehe. They're cuddling close together... I wonder if they see us the same way as we see them.
Well... Shall we show them that we're cuddling close together, too？
Geez... You could do something like that without asking.
...Do you think they're staring at us？
Yeah... And there are more and more of them coming this way. Why's that？
I don't feel good about this. Let's get out of here, okay？
Ah, okay. Somehow, this is a little scary...
Ah... So cute... That kitten on the wall is so cute.
Eh？ Is it sleeping？ And look at its tail...
Hehe. It might be dreaming about chasing a mouse, huh？
Ah, it woke up... Hehe... It's looking around restlessly. I bet it really was dreaming.
Ah... I thought it was an ornament, but it's actually a dog. It's big.
Look how it's wagging its tail happily...
Sorry. This big sister already has this one to take care of. Hehe.
Look, right there... Aaaah, it went in there...
In there... You mean there's a peacock in there？
Is it someone's pet？ ...But do people raise peacocks as pets？ That's amazing.
Ah, that cloud... No, it disappeared.
That cloud looked just like you. I see... So you'll disappear someday, too...
Ah... Was that a shooting star？
In the middle of the day？
...Ah, I forgot to make a wish. What a waste...
What did you want to wish for？
Ah, something smells nice... What was that smell？
Smell？ I didn't smell anything... .Was it just your imagination？
Eh？ Come on, the smell was... I don't really know how to describe it.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. I only know that your hair smells nice...
Geez... That's like a surprise attack. You're so crafty.
Wait, it looks like it's going to rain... right？
I thought I could spend more time walking with you...
...Let's hurry and go before it starts raining, okay？
No. Even if it rains, we can share this umbrella, right...？ Hehe. Do you hate that？
Hmm... No, geez... Something got in my eyes...
No, this is bad. Can you take a look？
Ah, a junior high couple... Hehe, their faces are all red. They're cute.
If we met during junior high, we'd probably look like that too, right？
...I wonder. I think we'd be the same as we are now...
Hehe. It'd be nice if we could act as innocent as those kids every now and then, huh？
...I want us to be like that.
Look. That elderly couple over there. They must be husband and wife...
That's nice... If we can be like that when we get old, I'd be happy...
Ah, well... Do you happen to have a twin brother or a cousin that looks like you？
Okay then... I just saw a guy who looked exactly like you. That's why I was surprised.
...Hehe. Hey, that woman in the red dress is very pretty, right？
Yeah... She might be a model, right？ Look at her figure and the clothes she's wearing...
Hmph. So that's what you've been looking at, huh？
So cute...▼ Okay, because you're cute, I'll forgive you.
Come on. There was a girl who just ran by, right？
Yeah... Somehow, she was smiling happily, huh？
Could it be love？ Even for a small girl, when she's in love she can smile like that... right？
...Hehe. You protected me in such casual manner.
Now you make me feel very glad to be your girlfriend.
Okay... Well, this kind of makes me feel embarrassed...
Hey, look at that grandpa. He's so thin but he's riding a very big motorcycle.
Do you want to ride that kind of motorcycle, too？
A little bit, I think... Will you ride on the back of it if I get one？
Hehe, sure. But wouldn't it be a problem to travel by bike when our family members increase？
Ah, that car is so tiny, it looks like a toy car...
Yeah. The interior seems to be very small.
But I think a small car is easier to drive...
Hehe. Well, when I get a driver's license, will you let this big sister take you for a ride？
Eh？ That's an extremely expensive foreign car, right？
Well, I'm not sure. But I can tell that it's a luxurious car for sure.
I'd prefer a smaller and cheaper one... I don't know why people like those expensive cars.
Didn't you hear the sirens just a while ago？
Geez, if you keep spacing out like this, you might get in an accident. I don't want to see you in an ambulance, okay？
Look. It just passed by... Eh？ It was there just a second ago...
(She probably mistook it for something else...)
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, wait a moment. My shoelaces are getting loose.
A lion... Ah, a costume？ No, it can't be. Why is it walking there...？ And with that collar？
What's wrong？ I think you just saw something impossible.
Ah, right. Have you heard of a giant turtle that moves at high speed？
Do you mean you've seen that legendary, high-speed giant turtle？
...Yes, just now... It must've been a dream. Yeah, it must've been a dream. A dream.
(Did you mistake it for something else...？)
J-Just now... That car-sized cockroach... No, it's nothing. Yeah, it's really nothing.
That's why I said it was nothing！ A cockroach can't be that big... And it was flying... That's impossible.
That person just now was that film director... The famous one who made many horror films that are known worldwide.
Didn't you just mistake someone else for him？ You don't have to be this disappointed...
Okay... But I should have asked for a handshake, at least...
That was dangerous... Who dropped this thing？
